data.description: Welcome to your spacious and inviting new home in beautiful Millsboro, Delaware! This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath condo/townhouse offers an incredible opportunity for first-time home buyers or those looking to relocate without breaking the bank. Plus, the icing on the cake? This home qualifies for USDA financing, which means a zero percent down payment option is on the table! Don't forget to ask us about the numerous grant programs available – your dream home may be even more affordable than you think.  Upon entering, you'll be greeted by a generous layout that boasts tons of space for your family and lifestyle needs. The large sunroom is the perfect spot to unwind with a book or enjoy your morning coffee. The spacious kitchen eating area is ideal for family gatherings and entertaining friends. Convenience is key with a convenient half bath located downstairs, and there are two full baths upstairs for added comfort and functionality.  Your one-car garage provides secure parking and storage space for your belongings.  Location is everything, and this home doesn't disappoint. You'll find yourself close to shopping, restaurants, and the charming town of Millsboro, making daily errands and dining out a breeze. And if you're dreaming of sunny days at the beach, you're in luck – you're less than 30 minutes away from the stunning beaches of Ocean City and Delaware.  As if that wasn't enough, this community offers fantastic amenities, including an outdoor pool for those hot summer days, a fitness center to help you stay active and healthy, and well-lit streets perfect for evening strolls and outings.  Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make this spacious, budget-friendly home yours. Schedule your showing today and start enjoying the coastal Delaware lifestyle!
